+om samvedi: Pracchin aur Maddhyakaalin Bharat mein Muslim Humlaawaroin se 
pehle Bengal ke Mahaan Pala, Sen, Chandra, Dev aur Goud Samrajya lag bhag 
purre Hindustan mein tha joh Madharchod, Behenchod, Ranndi ki Aulaad. 
Bengaliyoun ne Sarvaadda Iss mulk ke liye apni Kurbaani di thi aur aaage 
bhi dette raheinge. Humaari Waafaadari par shaqqkk matt kar Kutte. Bharaat 
Maata Rashha ke liye hum hasstein hastein apni Praanoin ki Aahuti de dennge 
lekin Gaddari ka Kalannk apne Maate par kabhi bardaast kareinngey. Indian 
Armed Forces mein bhi kittne Bengali logoin ne apne pranoin ki aahuti di 
hai. Mamta Banerjee Raanndi hai isska yeh matlab nahin tuu purri 
Bengaliyoun ko Gaali de. 
